        [
            "Pidigan, officially the Municipality of Pidigan (Ilocano: Ili ti Pidigan; Tagalog: Bayan ng Pidigan), is a 5th class municipality in the province of Abra, Philippines.",
            "According to the 2020 census, it has a population of 12,475 people."
        ],
        [
            "Geography"
        ],
        [
            "Pidigan is located at 17\u00b034\u2032N 120\u00b035\u2032E\ufeff / \ufeff17.57\u00b0N 120.59\u00b0E\ufeff / 17.57; 120.59."
        ],
        [
            "According to the Philippine Statistics Authority, the municipality has a land area of 49.15 square kilometres (18.98\u00a0sq\u00a0mi)\u2009 constituting 1.18% of the 4,165.25-square-kilometre- (1,608.21\u00a0sq\u00a0mi) total area of Abra."
        ],
        [
            "Pidigan is 8 kilometres (5.0\u00a0mi) from Bangued and 400 kilometres (250\u00a0mi) from Manila."
        ],
